[OVERLAY] VimFu — Quitting Vim
[SAY] How do you quit Vim? The most famous question in programming.
[SAY] Let's open a file.
[LINE] 'nvim hello.py'

              1         2         3         
    0123456789012345678901234567890123456789
    ────────────────────────────────────────
 0 │➜  vimfu nvim hello.py                  │
    ────────────────────────────────────────

[SAY] To quit, type colon Q.
[TYPE] ':q'

